cs.GT, cs.EC, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.CE 

This paper deals with game theory and mechanism design in the context of electricity markets. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Mechanism Design), followed by cs.EC (Economics and Computation) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization and mathematical modeling, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
